CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1783703991
OL,3,CLondon mayor's office blocking Met
OL,4,Cdeal was unlawful, court documents
OL,5,Cclaim
OL,7,FPart of London mayor Sir Sadiq Khan's
OL,8,Foffice unlawfully blocked the
OL,9,FMetropolitan Police's #50 million deal
OL,10,Fwith technology firm Palantir "because
OL,11,Fof an alleged mismatch between
OL,12,FPalantir's 'values and ethics' and
OL,13,F'London's values'", High Court
OL,14,Fdocuments claim.
OL,16,FPalantir, founded by tech magnate
OL,17,FPeter Thiel, is suing the Mayor's
OL,18,FOffice for Policing and Crime (Mopac)
OL,19,Fafter it refused to approve the deal
OL,20,Fearlier this year.
OL,26,@rD@_OUuD@RO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
