OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1783703991
OL,3,CLondon mayor's office blocking Met
OL,4,Cdeal was unlawful, court documents
OL,5,Cclaim
OL,7,FA spokesperson for the Mayor of London
OL,8,Fsaid: "On May 21 2026, the Deputy
OL,9,FMayor for Policing and Crime declined
OL,10,Fapproval for the Met to award a
OL,11,Fcontract worth up to #50m with
OL,12,Ftechnology firm Palantir to deliver a
OL,13,Fsystem called Unified Operational
OL,14,FAnalytics."
OL,16,F"This decision is subject to legal
OL,17,Fchallenge.
OL,19,F"We continue to robustly defend this
OL,20,Fdecision, made in line with our
OL,21,Fstatutory responsibilities."
OL,26,@pD@GOUvD@KO]xD@AOU{D@AOU}D@\O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G11/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1783703991
OL,3,CLondon mayor's office blocking Met
OL,4,Cdeal was unlawful, court documents
OL,5,Cclaim
OL,7,FIn written submissions for Thursday's
OL,8,Fhearing, Joseph Barrett KC, for Mopac,
OL,9,Fsaid Palantir has "provided no
OL,10,Fevidence whatever" to support its
OL,11,Fclaims, and that the body's decision
OL,12,Fnot to approve the deal was "obviously
OL,13,Fwithin the range of options" open to
OL,14,Fit.
OL,26,@qD@SOUrD@RO]tD@]OUuD@\O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G12/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1783703991
OL,3,CLondon mayor's office blocking Met
OL,4,Cdeal was unlawful, court documents
OL,5,Cclaim
OL,7,FHe continued that Mopac and the Met
OL,8,Fwere "working together on a new,
OL,9,Fcompetitive procurement" for the
OL,10,Fcontract, and that Palantir is "free,
OL,11,Fand indeed positively welcomed, to
OL,12,Fparticipate in this new, lawful and
OL,13,Ftransparent competitive process".
OL,15,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,16,Four political experts are across all
OL,17,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,18,Fto the latest episode below...
OL,26,@pD@FOUqD@XO]rD@`OUuD@`O]
